org.sidoh.wwf_api
Class Bag

java.lang.Object
  org.sidoh.wwf_api.Bag

public class Bag
extends java.lang.Object

Implements WWF's bag functionality. This is how game state is determined. A bag is initialized with a random number seed, and popped off of accordingly.
